title: Dirty Mary Crazy Larry
description:
Dirty Mary Crazy Larry (1974)



# Actors: Peter Fonda, Susan George, Adam Roarke, Kenneth Tobey, Eugene Daniels, 

# Directors: John Hough

Plot Synopsis: Mary and Larry are two lovers who, with Larry\&#039;s ace mechanic, kidnap the daughter of a grocery story owner, and make off with the ransom. They are chased over hill, over vale by the cops, who deploy everything from 426 Hemis to helicopters to stop Larry\&#039;s Dodge Charger. Except Mary was not with them when the kidnap took place.
